describe.en: A monkey is wearing a green shirt. The monkey has brown hair and big eyes. There is a blue sky behind the monkey.
describe.zh: 一隻猴子穿著綠色襯衫。這隻猴子有棕色毛髮和大眼睛。牠的身後是藍天。

describe.en: A man is standing in a field of yellow flowers. He is wearing a brown suit and a red tie. There are trees in the field behind him.

describe.en: A cat is being washed in a shower. The cat has brown eyes and a pink nose. It is wet and has long whiskers. There are water droplets coming from the shower head. A pair of hands is holding the cat.
describe.zh: 一隻貓正在淋浴下被清洗。牠有棕色的眼睛和粉紅色的鼻子。全身濕透，鬍鬚很長。蓮蓬頭正噴出水滴，一雙手正抱著這隻貓。
